---
import BaseLayout from '@layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import { SITE } from '@lib/config';
---

<BaseLayout title="about" description={`About ${SITE.author}`}>
  <section class="container about">
    <h1># about</h1>

    <pre class="ascii" aria-hidden="true">
{`$ cat /etc/motd

   name        : Marcos Magno Biriba Ribeiro (Marc)
   born        : 2005-01-18, São Paulo, Brazil
   based       : Switzerland
   interests   : guitar, homelab, self-hosting, security
   contact     : hello@marc-os.com`}
    </pre>

    <p>
      Hi — I'm Marc. My family names reflect my heritage: Ribeiro is my father's surname,
      and Biriba comes from my mother's side. I've lived in Brazil, Hungary, and now
      Switzerland, picking up English, a touch of Hungarian, and working on German along
      the way.
    </p>

    <p>
      My first spark for technology ignited between 8 and 13 — I taught myself to build
      an automatic door in Minecraft using command blocks, customised to recognise only
      my in-game name. My apprenticeship in software development started on August 2nd 2021,
      inspired by my dad's career. I believe perseverance is the key to overcoming any
      obstacle — learning a new language, adapting to a new country, or diving into complex
      technical challenges.
    </p>

    <h2>## this site</h2>
    <p>
      Built with <a href="https://astro.build" rel="noopener">Astro</a>. Content is plain
      markdown in <code>src/content/</code>. Themed with
      <a href="https://catppuccin.com" rel="noopener">Catppuccin Mocha</a>.
      No JS frameworks, no third-party trackers, no analytics, no databases.
    </p>
    <p>
      Hosted on a single VPS, served by a hardened container fronted by
      Nginx Proxy Manager. Source is on <a href={SITE.social.github} rel="noopener">GitHub</a>.
    </p>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .about { padding: 2rem 1.25rem 3rem; }
  .about h1 { margin-top: 0; }
  .ascii {
    color: var(--ctp-teal);
    font-size: 0.82rem;
    background: var(--bg-deep);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: var(--radius);
    padding: 1rem 1.2rem;
    margin: 1.5rem 0;
  }
  strong { color: var(--accent); font-weight: 600; }
</style>
